quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  39,22,"“Kodi amene Allah watsekula chifuwa chake povomereza Chisilamu, kotero kuti iye akuyenda mkuunika kwa Mbuye wake, (angafanane ndi yemwe akunyozera kupenyetsetsa zisonyezo za Allah?) Kuonongeka kwakukulu kuli pa ouma mitima yawo posakumbukira Allah (ndi kulabadira Qur’an). Iwo ali m’kusokera koonekera"
  39,23,"“Allah wavumbulutsa nkhani yabwino zedi yomwe ndi buku logwirizana nkhani zake; (losasemphana). Lobwerezabwereza (malamulo ake). Makungu a omwe amaopa Mbuye wawo amanjenjemera ndi ilo. Kenako makungu awo ndi mitima yawo zimakhazikika pokumbukira Allah. Buku limeneli ndi chiongoko cha Allah; ndi ilo, akumuongola amene wamfuna. Ndipo amene Allah wamulekelera kuti asokere (chifukwa chonyozera kwake choona), sangakhale ndi womuongola (ndi ompulumutsa ku chionongeko)"
  39,24,"“Kodi yemwe adzakhala akudzitchinjiriza ndi nkhope yake (uku manja atanjatidwa) ku chilango choipa pa tsiku la Qiyâma, (angafanane ndi yemwe adzakhala mchisangalalo mminda ya mtendere?” Ndipo kudzanenedwa kwa oipa: “Lawani zoipa za zochita zanu.”)"
  39,25,"“Amene adalipo patsogolo pawo, adatsutsa. Ndipo chilango chidawadzera kuchokera komwe sadali kuyembekezera"
  39,26,“Choncho Allah adawalawitsa kunyozeka pa moyo wa pa dziko lapansi; koma ndithu chilango cha tsiku la chimaliziro nchachikulu zedi (kuposa chilango cha m’dziko lapansi) akadakhala akudziwa
  39,27,“Ndithu m’buku ili la Qur’an taperekamo mafanizo osiyanasiyana kwa anthu kuti akumbukire
  39,28,"“Qur’an ya Chiarabu yopanda zokhota, kuti iwo aope (Allah)"
  39,29,"“Allah wapereka fanizo la munthu wotumikira mabwana awiri omwe ngokangana pa za iye, ndi munthu yemwe akutumikira bwana mmodzi. Kodi awiriwa ngofanana? Kuyamikidwa konse nkwa Allah! Koma ambiri a iwo sadziwa"
  39,30,“Ndithu iwe udzafa; naonso adzafa
  39,31,"“(Ndipo) kenako, inu patsiku la Qiyâma mudzakangana pamaso pa Mbuye wanu"